The paper addresses the problem of information retrieval, which is a core topic in the field of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also uses long short term memory (LSTM) to capture contextual dependencies, which is a technique commonly used in natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning (ML) fields such as computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.IR, followed by cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.NE.
